channel.title: Task 1: Intro and Starter Code :: Introduction to Web Dev
channel.description: This task puts your unit testing, modules making, and exception handling knowledge to use by writing tests and classes for the Mars rover named Curiosity. You will create a simulation for issuing commands to Curiosity. The idea is to create a command at mission control, convert that command into a message, send it to the rover, then have the rover respond to that message.
